data.description: Welcome to your recently remodeled 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home in Tampa! This 1,486 sqft corner lot property boasts high-impact windows, ceramic tile throughout, a newer shingle roof, and a 2018 central AC upgrade. Enjoy the convenience of being close to the airport, beaches, shopping centers, supermarkets, and the Veterans Expressway. The newly renovated kitchen features granite countertops. The fenced yard offers privacy, making it an ideal family home in a fantastic location.
